#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/business_loan_calculator.html:238
msgid "What is the Business Loan Calculator?"
msgstr ""

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/business_loan_calculator.html:240
msgid ""
"This calculator estimates payments and costs for business term loans, SBA "
"7(a) loans, and lines of credit. You can also compare multiple financing "
"options side by side for a given loan amount."
msgstr ""

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/business_loan_calculator.html:243
msgid ""
"Term loans and SBA loans show monthly (or periodic) payment, total interest, "
"fees, and total cost. Line of credit mode shows payoff time and total "
"interest for your current balance and payment. Compare mode shows payment "
"and total cost for several common loan scenarios."
msgstr ""

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/business_loan_calculator.html:250
msgid "Periodic / Monthly Payment"
msgstr ""

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/business_loan_calculator.html:251
msgid ""
"The fixed amount you pay each period. Term loans can be calculated for "
"monthly, biweekly, or weekly frequency."
msgstr ""

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/business_loan_calculator.html:254
#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/personal_loan_calculator.html:350
msgid "Total Interest & Total Cost"
msgstr ""

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/business_loan_calculator.html:255
msgid ""
"Total interest is the cost of borrowing. Total cost includes interest plus "
"any origination or guarantee fees."
msgstr ""

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/business_loan_calculator.html:258
msgid "SBA Guarantee Fee"
msgstr ""

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/business_loan_calculator.html:259
msgid ""
"SBA 7(a) loans may include a guarantee fee based on loan size; the "
"calculator applies a simplified fee structure."
msgstr ""

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/business_loan_calculator.html:266
msgid ""
"Choose loan type: Term Loan, SBA Loan, Line of Credit, or Compare Options."
msgstr ""

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/business_loan_calculator.html:267
msgid ""
"Enter loan amount, rate, and term (or for LOC: credit limit, balance, rate, "
"payment)."
msgstr ""

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/business_loan_calculator.html:268
msgid "For term loans, optionally set origination fee and payment frequency."
msgstr ""

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/business_loan_calculator.html:269
msgid ""
"Click Calculate to see payment, total interest, fees, and total cost (or "
"comparison table)."
msgstr ""

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/business_loan_calculator.html:274
msgid ""
"Term loan and SBA results show your periodic payment, effective APR, and a "
"summary of loan amount, interest, fees, and total cost. Line of credit "
"results show available credit, utilization, and months to payoff at your "
"entered payment. Compare mode shows several common business loan scenarios "
"(e.g. bank term, SBA, online lender) for your loan amount."
msgstr ""

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/business_loan_calculator.html:281
msgid ""
"Results are estimates. Actual terms, rates, and fees depend on your lender "
"and credit profile."
msgstr ""

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/business_loan_calculator.html:285
msgid ""
"SBA 7(a) loans are subject to eligibility and guarantee rules. Compare "
"offers from multiple lenders."
msgstr ""

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/business_loan_calculator.html:292
msgid ""
"Compare term length and frequency: shorter terms usually mean less total "
"interest."
msgstr ""

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/business_loan_calculator.html:293
msgid ""
"Factor origination and guarantee fees into total cost when comparing loans."
msgstr ""

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/business_loan_calculator.html:294
msgid ""
