#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/college_cost_calculator.html:197
msgid "What is the College Cost Calculator?"
msgstr ""

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/college_cost_calculator.html:199
msgid ""
"This calculator projects how much college will cost in the future based on "
"today's average costs (tuition, room & board, books, other) and an inflation "
"rate. You enter your child's current age, type of college (public in-state, "
"out-of-state, private, or community), and number of years. It shows total "
"projected cost and, if you enter current savings and expected return, how "
"much to save each month to close the gap."
msgstr ""

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/college_cost_calculator.html:208
msgid ""
"Today's average cost is inflated each year until the first year of college. "
"Total cost is the sum of all years of college at those projected amounts."
msgstr ""

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/college_cost_calculator.html:212
msgid ""
"The amount still needed after your current savings grow at the expected "
"return until college starts. Monthly savings needed is calculated to fill "
"this gap."
msgstr ""

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/college_cost_calculator.html:215
msgid "Savings projection"
msgstr ""

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/college_cost_calculator.html:216
msgid ""
"Shows how your balance grows year by year with assumed contributions and "
"investment return. Use it to see if you're on track."
msgstr ""

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/college_cost_calculator.html:224
msgid ""
"Enter your child's current age (0–18). Years until college = 18 minus age."
msgstr ""

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/college_cost_calculator.html:225
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Select college type and number of years (e.g. 4). Set an education inflation "
"rate (often 5%%%% or higher)."
msgstr ""

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/college_cost_calculator.html:226
msgid ""
"Optionally enter current savings and expected annual return to see monthly "
"savings needed and projection."
msgstr ""

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/college_cost_calculator.html:227
msgid ""
"Click Calculate to see total cost, breakdown, year-by-year costs, and "
"savings plan."
msgstr ""

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/college_cost_calculator.html:228
msgid "Use the charts to compare cost by category and by year."
msgstr ""

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/college_cost_calculator.html:235
msgid "Projected total cost"
msgstr ""

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/college_cost_calculator.html:235
msgid ""
"Sum of all years of college at inflated prices. This is the target amount to "
"fund."
msgstr ""

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/college_cost_calculator.html:236
msgid "Monthly savings needed"
msgstr ""

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/college_cost_calculator.html:236
msgid ""
"The fixed monthly contribution that, with your current savings growing at "
"the expected return, would close the funding gap by the time college starts."
msgstr ""

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/college_cost_calculator.html:237
msgid "Cost breakdown and by year"
msgstr ""

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/college_cost_calculator.html:237
msgid ""
"First-year cost is split into tuition, room & board, books, other. The year-"
"by-year table shows how each college year's cost increases with inflation."
msgstr ""

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/college_cost_calculator.html:244
msgid ""
"A doughnut chart of projected first-year cost: tuition, room & board, books, "
"other. Based on today's averages inflated to the first year of college."
msgstr ""

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/college_cost_calculator.html:245
msgid ""
"Bar chart of projected cost for each year of college. Later years are higher "
"due to inflation."
msgstr ""

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/college_cost_calculator.html:246
msgid ""
"Line chart of your savings balance over the years until college, assuming "
"you contribute the recommended monthly amount and earn the expected return."
msgstr ""

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/college_cost_calculator.html:253
msgid ""
"Costs are based on national averages. Actual costs vary by school and state."
msgstr ""

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/college_cost_calculator.html:254
msgid ""
"Consider 529 plans, financial aid, and scholarships. This tool does not "
"include aid or tax benefits."
msgstr ""

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/college_cost_calculator.html:255
msgid ""
