msgid "Avalanche vs Snowball"
msgstr ""

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/credit_cards_payoff_calculator.html:302
msgid ""
"Avalanche (highest APR first) saves the most interest. Snowball (smallest "
"balance first) pays off one card quickly and can boost motivation with early "
"wins."
