msgid ""
"Time to payoff for current debts is estimated using your entered monthly "
"payments. The consolidation loan amount is the sum of all debt balances plus "
"any fees. If the consolidation rate is lower than your weighted average rate "
"and the term is reasonable, you often save both monthly and total interest."
msgstr ""

