msgid ""
"The hero card shows whether you have a marriage bonus (savings) or penalty "
"(extra tax) and the amount. The comparison table shows tax per person as "
"single, combined single tax, and married filing jointly. The chart compares "
"tax under Singles, MFJ, and MFS. Use the “Why This Happens” note for a short "
"explanation based on your income split."
msgstr ""

