"budgets depend on your situation."
msgstr ""

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/rent_calculator.html:287
msgid ""
"Factor in renters insurance, parking, and moving costs (first month, last "
"month, security deposit) when planning."
msgstr ""

