msgid "For education only. Not tax or legal advice."
msgstr ""

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/rmd_calculator.html:334
#, python-format
msgid ""
"You can withdraw more than your RMD; the excess does not count toward future "
"years. Estimated tax in the results assumes a 22%%%% rate; your actual rate "
"may differ. Consider QCDs (qualified charitable distributions) if you are "
"70½+ to satisfy RMD with tax-free gifts."
msgstr ""

