"Enter current annual salary and a raise as a percentage or dollar amount. "
"Results show new salary, raise amount, percentage increase, and approximate "
"monthly and per-paycheck increase."
msgstr ""

#: Financial_Calculators/templates/financial_calculators/salary_calculator.html:425
msgid ""
"Enter two offers (amount and period for each). The calculator converts both "
"to annual and shows which is better and by how much."
msgstr ""

