"(calories) and serves unique functions in your body."
msgstr ""

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:328
msgid "Total Calories = Protein + Fat + Carbs"
msgstr ""

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:331
msgid ""
"Protein and carbohydrates provide 4 calories per gram, while fat provides 9 "
"calories per gram. Understanding your macro breakdown helps you optimize "
"your diet for your specific goals."
msgstr ""

#: Fitness_and_Health_Calculators/templates/fitness_and_health_calculators/macro_calculator.html:337
