"1/8 = 0.125."
msgstr ""

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/exponent_calculator.html:128
msgid "What is a fractional exponent?"
msgstr ""

#: Math_Calculators/templates/math_calculators/exponent_calculator.html:131
msgid ""
"A fractional exponent represents a root. For example, 8^(1/3) = ∛8 = 2, "
"which is the cube root of 8."
