#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/age_calculator.html:435
msgid "Life Progress Gauge"
msgstr ""

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/age_calculator.html:437
msgid ""
"A circular gauge chart displaying your life progress percentage. The filled "
"portion represents the percentage of an average 80-year lifespan you've "
"lived, while the unfilled portion shows the remaining percentage."
msgstr ""

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/age_calculator.html:445
msgid "Age Calculation Method"
msgstr ""

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/age_calculator.html:447
msgid ""
"Our calculator uses precise date arithmetic to determine age. The "
"calculation accounts for:"
