#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/circle_skirt_calculator.html:171
msgid "How Circle Skirts Work"
msgstr ""

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/circle_skirt_calculator.html:172
msgid ""
"A circle skirt is cut from a circular piece of fabric with a hole for the "
"waist. The waist radius determines the size of the inner circle, and the "
"outer radius includes the desired skirt length plus hem allowance. Different "
"fractions of a circle create different levels of flare and fullness."
