"Temperature (4 units), Volume (14 units), Area (10 units), Speed (7 units), "
"Time (12 units), Digital Storage (14 units), Pressure (9 units), and Energy "
"(10 units)."
msgstr ""

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/conversion_calculator.html:494
msgid ""
"All conversions use internationally recognized conversion factors for "
"maximum accuracy."
msgstr ""

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/conversion_calculator.html:500
msgid ""
"Temperature conversions use direct formulas rather than simple "
"multiplication factors."
msgstr ""

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/conversion_calculator.html:506
msgid ""
"Digital storage uses both SI (KB, MB) and binary (KiB, MiB) standards. SI "
"units use base-1000, binary units use base-1024."
