msgid "What is GDP?"
msgstr ""

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/gdp_calculator.html:235
msgid ""
"Gross Domestic Product (GDP) is the total monetary value of all finished "
"goods and services produced within a country's borders in a specific time "
"period. It serves as a comprehensive measure of economic performance and is "
"used to compare economic output of different countries. GDP can be "
"calculated using expenditure, income, and production (value-added) "
"approaches."
