#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/snow_day_calculator.html:318
msgid ""
"A snow day is a day when schools and sometimes businesses close due to "
"severe winter weather conditions like heavy snowfall, ice storms, or extreme "
"cold. This calculator uses multiple weather and environmental factors to "
"estimate the probability of your school calling a snow day."
msgstr ""

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/snow_day_calculator.html:324
msgid "How This Calculator Works"
msgstr ""

#: Other_Calculators/templates/other_calculators/snow_day_calculator.html:326
